      <header>custom PWM complementary flags for output pins</header>
      <description><para>This flag can be used with any of the <computeroutput>pwm_pin_set_*</computeroutput> API calls to indicate that the PWM signal has to be routed to the complementary output channel.</para>
<para>This feature is only available on certain SoC families, refer to the binding&apos;s documentation for more details. The custom flags are on the upper 8bits of the pwm_flags_t </para>
</description>
